
-------------------------------------------
|||| Jira PLugin Installation ||||
-------------------------------------------


Default:
 - twister server side path: /opt/twister
 - twister client side path: /home/user/twister


	---- SERVER side ----

1. sudo cp /path/to/JiraPlugin/Jira /opt/twister/plugins

2. vim /path/to/twister/config/plugins.xml

append config:

<Plugin>
	<name>JIRA</name>
	<jarfile>Jira/JiraPlugin.jar</jarfile>
	<pyfile>Jira/JiraPlugin.py</pyfile>
	<status>enabled</status>
</Plugin>

